network.param.modules.person.contacts

Class Contact

  • java.lang.Object
    • network.param.modules.person.contacts.Contact
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IBean, IContact

    public class Contact
extends java.lang.Object
implements IContact
    Implementation of IContact, this class represents the contact.

    This interface IContact will represents contact information. IContact defines below few categories of operations:

    • setParamID method for set customer unique ParamID.

    • setName method for set contact name.

    • setOrganization method for set contact organization.

    • setEmail method for set contact Email.

    • setAddress method for set contact address.

    • getName method for set contact tags.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
